{
  "text": "The higher the initial MIC of strains the more rapidly they might be adapted to rising concentrations of disinfectants, as shown by [CITATION_1] . Therefore, we performed additionally an exploratory adaptation test with the DSM 2570 reference strain and three strains with DDAC_MICs > 1.4 mg/l.",
